/use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Nov 28, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104cvk1665702766970.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/cvk1665702766970.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/cvk1665702766970.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"cvk1665702766970\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      message\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"cvk1665702766970__message_66423\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Display the text of a message. </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"cvk1665702766970__topic_d19454e1_d19455e1_d19456e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"cvk1665702766970__p_d19457e1_d19458e1_d19459e1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">MESsage</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">MessageId</var>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"cvk1665702766970__topic_d14007e1_d14008e1_d14009e1_d14010e1_d14011e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d919026e65\">\n                        \n Arguments\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"cvk1665702766970__p_d19463e1_d19464e1_d19465e1\"><var class=\"keyword varname\">MessageId</var>—identifier of a text\n            message in the current library and language.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"cvk1665702766970__topic_d14012e1_d14013e1_d14014e1_d14015e1_d14016e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d919026e76\">\n                        \n Description\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"cvk1665702766970__p_d19469e1_d19470e1_d19471e1\">Display the text for message MessageId, that is <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$text</span>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">(<var class=\"keyword varname\">MessageId</var>)</code>, in the message frame and on the message line.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"cvk1665702766970__p_d19472e1_d19473e1_d19474e1\">If the <var class=\"keyword varname\">MessageId</var> cannot be found,\n            no message is displayed.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"cvk1665702766970__section_wns_p4b_tcc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d919026e100\">Example:</h2>\n<div class=\"div\">\n<p class=\"p\">Show the text of message 6865 in the current library and language:</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"cvk1665702766970__pre_rzd_x4b_tcc\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">mes 6865</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2526638\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2526638\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "message Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Nov 28, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 message Display the text of a message. MESsage MessageId Arguments MessageId —identifier of a text message in the current library and language. Description Display the text for message MessageId, that is $text ( MessageId ) , in the message frame and on the message line. If the MessageId cannot be found, no message is displayed. Example: Show the text of message 6865 in the current library and language: mes 6865 Copy Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}